66666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/e0dd3c116e5e8d8cddbd3815ac684d03/8ac56/bemypet.webp 240w,\n/static/e0dd3c116e5e8d8cddbd3815ac684d03/d3be9/bemypet.webp 480w,\n/static/e0dd3c116e5e8d8cddbd3815ac684d03/e46b2/bemypet.webp 960w,\n/static/e0dd3c116e5e8d8cddbd3815ac684d03/f992d/bemypet.webp 1440w,\n/static/e0dd3c116e5e8d8cddbd3815ac684d03/8641a/bemypet.webp 1856w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/e0dd3c116e5e8d8cddbd3815ac684d03/8ff5a/bemypet.png 240w,\n/static/e0dd3c116e5e8d8cddbd3815ac684d03/e85cb/bemypet.png 480w,\n/static/e0dd3c116e5e8d8cddbd3815ac684d03/d9199/bemypet.png 960w,\n/static/e0dd3c116e5e8d8cddbd3815ac684d03/07a9c/bemypet.png 1440w,\n/static/e0dd3c116e5e8d8cddbd3815ac684d03/6fa81/bemypet.png 1856w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/e0dd3c116e5e8d8cddbd3815ac684d03/d9199/bemypet.png\"\n          alt=\"bemypet\"\n          title=\"bemypet\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>반려견 동반으로 갈 수 있는 장소들을 한눈에 모아볼 수 있는 사이트</li>\n<li>\n<p>주요 기능</p>\n<ul>\n<li>장소, 상호명, 태그 등으로 검색</li>\n<li>방문했던 장소들의 평점과 좋아요 및 리뷰 기능</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>‘첫 프로젝트 잘해보자!’ 했는데 크롤링 3일차에 사이트가 리뉴얼중이었는지 멈춰버려서,\n엎어버린 비운의 0.5 프로젝트이다..</p>\n<h2 id=\"롤렉스-프로젝트\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A1%A4%EB%A0%89%EC%8A%A4-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"롤렉스 프로젝트 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>롤렉스 프로젝트</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0e2ecf3b60fa9b2d9778030c3b0634ee/ab40b/rolex.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/0e2ecf3b60fa9b2d9778030c3b0634ee/8ac56/rolex.webp 240w,\n/static/0e2ecf3b60fa9b2d9778030c3b0634ee/d3be9/rolex.webp 480w,\n/static/0e2ecf3b60fa9b2d9778030c3b0634ee/e46b2/rolex.webp 960w,\n/static/0e2ecf3b60fa9b2d9778030c3b0634ee/f992d/rolex.webp 1440w,\n/static/0e2ecf3b60fa9b2d9778030c3b0634ee/0eeae/rolex.webp 1736w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/0e2ecf3b60fa9b2d9778030c3b0634ee/8ff5a/rolex.png 240w,\n/static/0e2ecf3b60fa9b2d9778030c3b0634ee/e85cb/rolex.png 480w,\n/static/0e2ecf3b60fa9b2d9778030c3b0634ee/d9199/rolex.png 960w,\n/static/0e2ecf3b60fa9b2d9778030c3b0634ee/07a9c/rolex.png 1440w,\n/static/0e2ecf3b60fa9b2d9778030c3b0634ee/ab40b/rolex.png 1736w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/0e2ecf3b60fa9b2d9778030c3b0634ee/d9199/rolex.png\"\n          alt=\"bemypet\"\n          title=\"bemypet\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>시계 브랜드</li>\n<li>\n<p>주요 기능</p>\n<ul>\n<li>원하는 시계로 커스터마이징</li>\n<li>시계 컬렉션 모아보기</li>\n<li>재료별로 필터 기능</li>\n<li>나의 셀렉션(좋아요 기능)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>팀 구성</p>\n<ul>\n<li>프론트엔드 3명, 백엔드 3명</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wecode-bootcamp-korea/Rolex-backend\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">프론트엔드 Github</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wecode-bootcamp-korea/Rolex-backend\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">백엔드 Github</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>적용 기술(백엔드)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Python</li>\n<li>Bcrypt</li>\n<li>JWT</li>\n<li>Django</li>\n<li>MySQL</li>\n<li>AWS EC2/RDS</li>\n<li>Trello</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"내가-담당한-부분\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%82%B4%EA%B0%80-%EB%8B%B4%EB%8B%B9%ED%95%9C-%EB%B6%80%EB%B6%84\" aria-label=\"내가 담당한 부분 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>내가 담당한 부분</h3>\n<p>(DB 모델링과 크롤링은 공동으로 담당하였다.)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>엔드포인트 구현</p>\n<ul>\n<li>회원가입</li>\n<li>로그인</li>\n<li>좋아요/좋아요 취소</li>\n<li>나의 셀렉션 목록</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"담당하지-않은-부분은\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8B%B4%EB%8B%B9%ED%95%98%EC%A7%80-%EC